Package: twfeivdecomp
Title: Instrumented Difference-in-Differences Decomposition
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sho", "Miyaji", email = "sho.miyaji@yale.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a decomposition of the two-way fixed effects instrumental variable estimator into all possible Wald DID estimators. Provides functions to summarize the contribution of different cohort comparisons to the overall TWFEIV estimate, with or without controls.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
